          The current database (via <Link
            url="https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4139722"
            label="Zenodo"
          />):
        </p>
        <Zenodo
          authors={["Mammal Diversity Database"]}
          year={year}
          title="Mammal Diversity Database (Version 1.13) [Data set]"
          doi="https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10595931"
        />
      </Section>
    </div>
  </MainPage></Layout
